title: Stosur into Hong Kong tennis third round
text:
Stosur into Hong Kong tennis third round 
Australian Samantha Stosur has won through to the quarter-finals of the Hong Kong Open. 
Fifth-seeded Stosur has accounted for Monica Puig of Puerto Rico 6-4 6-4. 
The Australian has set up a last-eight showdown with Britain’s Heather Watson, who’s survived a battle with qualifier Lee Ya-hsuan, winning 6-0 6-7 (5-7) 6-4.
